title: MUSIC: Yemi Alade – Classic Girl (Jidenna Cover)
content:
Yemi Alade releases Classic Girl, a cover of Jidenna’s Classic Man she performed for Factory 78. It was off as a freestyle but it has since been released online. 
 
Listen, download and tell us what you think about it.
